flowchart TB
    A[DOS application] --> B[INT 21h file call]
    B --> C[DOS file system]
    C --> D[INT 13h read sector N of virtual C:]
    D --> E[Stacker INT 13h hook]
    E --> F[Map sector N via cluster table]
    F --> G[Read compressed run from CVF on H:]
    G --> H[LZS decompress in RAM]
    H --> I[Return uncompressed sector]
    I --> C
    C --> B
    B --> A

    style E fill:#cfe8d4,stroke:#2a7a3a,color:#000
    style H fill:#d6e0f5,stroke:#3a5aa2,color:#000
